    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-569&quot; title=&quot;Category names with spaces cause NullPointerException in ConfusionMatrix when testing classifier&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MAHOUT-569&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MAHOUT-569&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Fix a certain NPE because labels/labelsMap go out of sync somehow&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
